text: Theo Bussiere (born 18 January 1995) is a French competitive swimmer. He competed for France in the 2016 Summer Olympics in the heats on the 4x100 meter relay. ==References== Category:French male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Male medley swimmers
